1.title: Mission Maria Island
1.plot: Three Tasmanian devil joeys, Reba, Remmy and Ruben, prepare to leave life in captivity for an adventure into the wild that may hold the key to the survival of their species.

2.title: Devil D Day
2.plot: Scientists put the Tasmanian devils through personality tests to make sure they can cope with the adventure that awaits them - and freedom for the first time - on remote Maria Island.

3.title: Meet the Neighbours
3.plot: As the newly released Tasmanian devils explore their new home on Maria Island, the hand-reared predators find the going tough and must dig deep to find the wild animal within.

4.title: Summer on Devil Island
4.plot: Three months after the release, the Tasmanian devils face the challenge of their lives with an influx of tourists and a record-breaking heat wave that could spell the end for these tough little predators.

5.title: Manny Goes Missing
5.plot: It's the breeding season but four months after releasing 15 Tasmanian devils on remote Maria Island, the scientists are worried. Manny the male who loves exploring is missing.

6.title: Devil Dynasty
6.plot: It's been five months since their release and the future looks bright for the 14 surviving disease free Tasmanian devils on Maria Island as all eight females prepare to have joeys.

imdb.plot outline: In a real life 'Madagascar', 50 mollycoddled Tasmanian Devils are hauled from the 5 star luxury of Australian zoos and cast away like convicts on a remote island to fend for themselves. Little do they realise the very fate of their kind rests on their shoulders. Since 1996 the Devil has fallen prey to a highly contagious facial cancer that has wiped out 80% of the wild population. Now, wildlife biologist Nick Mooney and his team have hatched an audacious plan to save these devilishly delightful little critters from extinction. They will create an 'insurance' population of disease-free Devils on the former penal settlement of Maria Island off the coast of Tasmania. It's a risky experiment - because 'disease-free' means 'captive' and the one hundred individuals they've handpicked from zoos and animal sanctuaries across Australia have never hunted for themselves, found shelter or faced a predator in their pampered little lives.
imdb.title: Devil Island
plot: These Devils were born in zoo heaven, now they're being shipped to hell.::Anonymous
